{"root":{"data":{"id":"d22skkc6im00","created":1718678189375,"text":"第九章 安全仪表系统设计应用"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22sln42rvs0","created":1718678273780,"text":"石油化工企业安全解决方案"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22slu89tds0","created":1718678289271,"text":"◼ 安全评估 （安全生命周期，风险评估，功能安全管理）；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22sm7skpio0","created":1718678318797,"text":"◼ 风险预防 （对人身、设备及环境的损害，重复事件减到最少）；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22sm7skxso0","created":1718678318797,"text":"◼ 安全仪表系统 （减少不必要的停车，故障原因分析，损失减少）；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22sm7skobk0","created":1718678318797,"text":"◼ 快速恢复生产 （缩短恢复生产时间，避免相同故障重复发生）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22smmjo2k80","created":1718678350910,"text":"石油化工企业安全生命周期"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22smsqmx8w0","created":1718678364392,"text":"• 风险评估"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqnqwo0","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 安全功能分配"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqnnf40","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 安全需求规格"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqndpc0","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 设计及其工程"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqnm3s0","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 安装、开车、确认"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqnsvc0","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 操作维护"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqnr3c0","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 修改或处理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqnk600","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 确认"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22smsqngko0","created":1718678364393,"text":"• 功能安全管理"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22sn0buuqo0","created":1718678380913,"text":"危险与可操作性审查"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22sn4gymm00","created":1718678389928,"text":"对生产装置的安全性和操作性进行设计审查;"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22sn8aszjs0","created":1718678398263,"text":"根据标准、工艺参数等按工艺流程（PID）进行系统分析，正常/非正常工况可能出现的问题、产生的原因、可能导致的后果及应采取的措施；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22snl49ug00","created":1718678426166,"text":" 有生产经验、工艺、安全、设备、电气、仪表、 环保、经济等专家共同研究； "},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22snv0d61k0","created":1718678447698,"text":"HAZOP作业流程:选择研究节点→选择工艺参数→ 选择引导词→发现有价值的偏差→分析产生偏差 的原因、后果及现有措施→评估风险→提出控制 风险建议。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22so2s7tfc0","created":1718678464620,"text":"安全保护级别分析"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22so9ba6zk0","created":1718678478833,"text":"• 集中研究后果严重和高频发事件；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22so9ba7vk0","created":1718678478833,"text":"• 考虑识别的引发事件和原因；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22so9baeps0","created":1718678478833,"text":"• 确认对各引发事件有效的保护层；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22so9b9x0o0","created":1718678478833,"text":"• 有效分配降低风险的资源；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22so9ba2uo0","created":1718678478833,"text":"• 确定安全仪表系统（SIL）等级"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22soe843ds0","created":1718678489525,"text":"安全仪表系统(SIS)"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22solaqgi80","created":1718678504921,"text":"安全仪表系统 (Safety Instrumented System - SIS)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22solapzk80","created":1718678504921,"text":"〔仪表保护系统(Instrument Protection System- IPS) 〕"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22solaq2kw0","created":1718678504921,"text":"〔安全联锁系统 (Safety Interlocking System - SIS) 〕"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22solaqgr40","created":1718678504921,"text":"〔紧急停车系统 (Emergency Shut-Down System - ESD) 〕"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22soqpscvk0","created":1718678516715,"text":"目前SIS采用标准规范"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22sozhy8eo0","created":1718678535833,"text":" IEC 61508   Functional Safety of electrical /electronic /programmable electronic safety-related system"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22spdg50bs0","created":1718678566198,"text":"IEC 61511 Functional Safety Instrumented system for the Process Industry Section"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22spqf6cww0","created":1718678594438,"text":" IEC 61131 Programmable Controllers"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22spxmpiww0","created":1718678610131,"text":"ANSI/ISA-84.01 Application of Safety Instrumented Systems for the Process Industries"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22sq4nyz6g0","created":1718678625445,"text":" DIN V 19250 Programmable Safety System "},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22sqai5c940","created":1718678638153,"text":"SH/T3018 石油化工安全仪表系统设计规范（中华人民 共和国石油化工行业标准） 目前SIS采用标准规范 Design code for safety instrumented system in petrochemical industry"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22sqnft0y80","created":1718678666310,"text":"SIS功能及要求"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22sqt5r5sw0","created":1718678678763,"text":"安全仪表系统（SIS）在生产装置的开车、停车阶段，运行以及维护操作期间，对人员健康、装置设备及环境提供安全保护。无论是生产装置本身出现的故障危险，还是人为因素导致的危险以及一些不可抗拒因素引发的危险，SIS系统都应立即作出正确反应并给出相应的逻辑信号，使生产装置安全联锁或停车，阻止危险的发生和事故的扩散，使危害减少到最小。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22sr82jqzk0","created":1718678711221,"text":"SIS 系 统 应 具 备 高 的 可 靠 性 （ Reliability) 、 可 用 性（Availability）和可维护性（Maintainability）。当SIS系统本身出现故障时仍能提供安全保护功能。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22srivg9z40","created":1718678734736,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}